---
title: Veggie Shepherd's Pie and Crispy Mash Potatoes
description: We love making simple, tasty meals! This veggie shepherds pie shouldn't disappoint. From the classic french flavours of a mirepoix to the fluffy mash topping; this hearty meal is both familiar and satisfying!
